Paper: hep-th/9705005

Date: 1997-05-02

Title: Lorentz Symmetry of Supermembrane in Light Cone Gauge Formulation

Authors: Kiyoshi Ezawa, Yutaka Matsuo, Koichi Murakami

Comments: 22 pages, Latex, appendix F added, reference added

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 98 (1997) 485-505

We prove the Lorentz symmetry of supermembrane theory in the light cone gaugeto complete the program initiated by de Wit, Marquard and Nicolai. We give somecomments on extending the formulation to the M(atrix) theory.